{"tid":1308554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"！！聽日，光復上水！！","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T19:37:26.000Z","uid":215042,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"242e40dc037153657284404f9c61f1178d2467dd","tid":1308554,"uid":215042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKcKSdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKcKSdQ.png&h=600245e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3bDcdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3bDcdR.png&h=c50293ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82UYcdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82UYcdR.png&h=5cfeebfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大唔好覺得上水好遠而唔嚟，最初水貨最嚴重就係上水，後來再蔓延到元朗、沙田，一日唔反抗，佢哋就會變本加厲！<br />\n<br />\n上水龍蛇雜混，如果少人班兄弟會好危險，所以麻煩大家幫推之剩都要身體力行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">附上實用資訊link</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[發夢] [詳細有圖] 夢見自己成為上水導遊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306479</a><br />\n<br />\n[突發][713光復上水]一封北區居民寫給香港人的公開信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dhvxJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dhvxJS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>713 光復上水詳情及注意事項：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午3:30開始<br />\n<br />\n起點：上水北區運動場<br />\n<br />\n衣著：建議黑衫，口罩 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYwoouN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYwoouN.png&h=30a52792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>交通</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗交通係大家最concern嘅野，大部份地區都有巴士入上水，不過要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">留意當日改道</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4O3uiYG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4O3uiYG.png&h=3c3d3ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8k7few2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8k7few2.png&h=e5a23561&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVRcgLn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVRcgLn.png&h=21a66f60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議大家可以睇翻九巴App嘅乘客通告<br />\n<br />\n未嚟過上水嘅巴絲打都唔使太擔心，因為上水好細，好容易行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一方有難，八方支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復上水消息發佈tg channel</span>：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Assemble713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAssemble713&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0ILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=f36d4127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Assemble713</a>"},{"pid":"628f8a8fb7b8e034e09ef46ce62763d64cdcc911","tid":1308554,"uid":215042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYxVY3W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYxVY3W.png&h=ec13db7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrAkqJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrAkqJX.png&h=38291f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvYVeCi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvYVeCi.png&h=a5e59f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbSCsXv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbSCsXv.png&h=d87c3c12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KyfXsXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKyfXsXw.png&h=6cb0b643&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UJRLBQS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUJRLBQS.png&h=2484d78d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuSSgQT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuSSgQT.png&h=864baab9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e68def3c1d7087eaf4b4de9972e6f0c2477c137","tid":1308554,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"我無野講!"},{"pid":"b71bcf960c28665f1d55b2e6d8b6d78c5ad798dc","tid":1308554,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:26:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adb0c03ffc1d9519a8c821388a0eb582914cfdd2","tid":1308554,"uid":215042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z11fY4X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz11fY4X.png&h=4d66138d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉至tg channel<br />\n<br />\n注意星期多條巴士線會14:00後改道<br />\n<br />\n73B(上水來往大埔循環線)：停北區公園北門後轉左上雞嶺返大埔<br />\n(最近落車點：北區公園北門)<br />\n(建議手足搭鐵)<br />\n<br />\n77K(上水來往元朗)： 改 *彩園* 做總站，不設其他加站<br />\n（最近落車點：臨時總站　彩園，即上水火車站附近）<br />\n<br />\n261（上水來往屯門）：改為屯門往上水 *循環線* ，經大頭嶺、翠麗迴旋處調頭返天水圍<br />\n臨時站：上水圍，寶石湖路，彩蒲苑彩顏閣<br />\n(最近落車點：寶石湖路)<br />\n<br />\n270B（上水來往奧運）<br />\n往上水：停完上官轉入清河做總站<br />\n往奧運：清河頭站，轉左去吳屋村回原路<br />\n(最近落車點：清河邨)<br />\n(建議手足搭鐵)<br />\n<br />\n276 276P（上水來往天水圍及元朗）：改為天水圍往上水 *循環綫* ，經大頭嶺、翠麗迴旋處調頭返天水圍<br />\n臨時站：上水圍，寶石湖路，彩蒲苑彩顏閣<br />\n(最近落車點：寶石湖路)<br />\n<br />\n277E（上水來往藍田站，經大老山）：<br />\n藍田方向：天平總站後直落清河<br />\n天平方向：到清河後加停北區醫院，上水官立中學，經雞嶺直落天平<br />\n(最近落車點：總站天平)<br />\n(建議手足搭鐵)<br />\n<br />\n278X（上水來往荃灣，經城門）：改以 *太平* 為總站<br />\n(最近落車點：臨時總站太平)<br />\n(建議手足搭鐵)<br />\n<br />\n279X（上水來往青衣，經大欖）：來回程改行彩園路<br />\n臨時站：青衣方向只停彩碧閣，聯和墟方向加停彩園路上水站<br />\n(最近落車點：上水站　＊注意上水站改為近彩園邨一方，不是平日近上水廣場)<br />\n<br />\n373（上水來往中環）：停北區公園後加停天平總站，以 *翠麗花園* 總站<br />\n(最近落車點：臨時總站翠麗花園)<br />\n673（上水來往中環）：改以 *翠麗花園* 為總站，香港方向加停天平總站，回程停天平後直去翠麗花園<br />\n(最近落車點：臨時總站翠麗花園)<br />\n（對面海的手足建議搭鐵或978，373/673兜埋粉嶺先落上水&hellip; 暈車浪）<br />\n（978係冇改道的,經西隧 於上水站落車）<br />\n<br />\nW 3：改以 *太平* 為總站<br />\n(最近落車點：臨時總站太平)<br />\n(建議手足搭鐵)<br />\n<br />\n以上只供參考，屆時請以在場外勤人員指示為準"},{"pid":"369ecd106a3816dc88a59382ad22b1bc8a51e52f","tid":1308554,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31ed70ba4bebe92c692adb75c274c56f32dabf2f","tid":1308554,"uid":276711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06289d85e108f480c0e0115ebf9cfc1b5caab9e9","tid":1308554,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:19.000Z","msg":"唔該哂 樓主幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4584ef1e4203c141200939ecaf6724e77fdc18ed","tid":1308554,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"69236d67946b3e42cbf6ca2ec93dad2c6d3bb8dd","tid":1308554,"uid":215042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f4dbed6257af883867757c25e7cf1d0bd0075b","tid":1308554,"uid":215042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd3d71f40eab17feeb8b5f8103bfd78e3ea5b49","tid":1308554,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"AirDrop 傳單可以加個網頁等大陸人睇多啲<br />\n<br />\n《反送中》小弟整左個網頁同D傳單 希望大家廣傳<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291864</a>"},{"pid":"12acbb38fb0cb77e0b202ea8713a8ea7b11d0d9e","tid":1308554,"uid":13387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"【推上熱門】713光復上水資料<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\